      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">15.101-3</ph> 	Tiered evaluation of small business offers.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="id202SCF0D09M" class="- topic/p ">An agency shall not create a tiered (or "cascading") evaluation of offers, as described in <xref href="https://www.govinfo.gov/content/pkg/CFR-2024-title13-vol1/xml/CFR-2024-title13-vol1-sec125-2.xml"
                  format="html"
                  scope="external"
                  class="- topic/xref ">13 CFR 125.2</xref>, for multiple-award contracts unless an agency has statutory authority.</p>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
